Each output folder contains an orignal video, its processed version (using our system) and a ROI json.

ROI json contains first 100 records, with no landmark data.
It serves as an example output only.
While in implemented system we support upto 1000 records per request, with in depth per frame landmark data.

The videos used in the tests are taken from: https://github.com/intel-iot-devkit/sample-videos
